  "description": "<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201308/3f49a92cb7144f1f83a1d2b3b090fde1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t大家好，我是沪江小D！</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t&ldquo;<strong>跟小D学新鲜热词</strong>&rdquo;，由小D我主讲，每周带领大家通过当下最fashion的事件来学习最in的单词~欢迎关注~</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t下面就开始吧~</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/f1c92d1391c54842a920d373bbf487f1.jpg\" /><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/f1c92d1391c54842a920d373bbf487f1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t2014年首期的《新闻联播》结尾时玩起了&ldquo;浪漫&rdquo;，向全国观众&ldquo;表白&rdquo;，要与观众一起&ldquo;传承一生一世的爱和正能量&rdquo;，网友们惊喜新闻联播也&ldquo;卖萌&rdquo;了，满满的都是爱。最近北大考古学教授卖萌吃鸡也在网络走红，那&ldquo;卖萌&rdquo;用英语该怎么表达呢？今天就和小D一起看下吧！</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t我们经常说的&ldquo;卖萌&rdquo;就是装可爱的意思，实际上卖萌是有褒义和贬义之分，褒义的卖萌表示展示自己可爱或者憨囧的状态，贬义的卖萌指做出常人理解范围的囧事，或者做出明知故犯的傻事等这类事情的统称。所以&ldquo;卖萌&rdquo;用英语可以表达为 <strong><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/play cute\" target=\"_blank\">play cute</a>/<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/being cute\" target=\"_blank\">being cute</a>/<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/act cute\" target=\"_blank\">act cute</a>/<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/play innocent\" target=\"_blank\">play innocent</a></strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<strong>例：</strong>Don't play cute with me!<br />\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #006400;\">不要给我卖萌！</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<strong>例：</strong>I know you're being cute.<br />\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #006400;\">我知道你在卖萌。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/7f11284dd3474b5380a06f9cc7214f67.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t&ldquo;卖萌&rdquo;也可以说成 <strong><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/give someone those puppy-dog eyes\" target=\"_blank\">give someone those puppy-dog eyes</a></strong>，就是像小狗一样卖萌装可怜，是不是很形象呢？</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t例：she gives me those puppy-dog eyes because she wants my help.<br />\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #006400;\">她在我面前卖萌装可怜，因为她想让我帮她。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t大家知道卖萌日是哪天吗？没错，就是十月十日啦，两个&ldquo;十&rdquo;并排组成&ldquo;艹&rdquo;，&ldquo;日&rdquo;、&ldquo;月&rdquo;二字组成&ldquo;明&rdquo;，十月十日就拼成了一个萌字，汉字真的是博大精深啊！</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/f1c92d1391c54842a920d373bbf487f1.jpg\" /><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/f1c92d1391c54842a920d373bbf487f1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/tag/%E8%B7%9F%E5%B0%8FD%E5%AD%A6%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E7%83%AD%E8%AF%8D/\" target=\"_blank\">点击查看往期&ldquo;跟小D学新鲜热词&rdquo;精彩内容&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\">以上内容由沪江小D团队编译制作，转载请注明出处。</span></span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p565066/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p565066\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"